#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.eval.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.eval"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.maxframe_eval:1 of
msgid "Evaluate a Python expression as a string using various backends."
msgstr "使用各种后端将 Python 表达式作为字符串进行求值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.maxframe_eval:3 of
msgid ""
"The following arithmetic operations are supported: ``+``, ``-``, ``*``, "
"``/``, ``**``, ``%``, ``//`` (python engine only) along with the "
"following boolean operations: ``|`` (or), ``&`` (and), and ``~`` (not). "
"Additionally, the ``'pandas'`` parser allows the use of :keyword:`and`, "
":keyword:`or`, and :keyword:`not` with the same semantics as the "
"corresponding bitwise operators.  :class:`~pandas.Series` and "
":class:`~pandas.DataFrame` objects are supported and behave as they would"
" with plain ol' Python evaluation."
msgstr ""
"支持以下算术运算：``+``、``-``、``*``、``/``、``**``、``%``、``//``（仅限"
" Python 引擎），以及以下布尔运算：``|``（或）、``&``（与）和 ``~``（非）"
"。此外，``'pandas'`` 解析器允许使用 :keyword:`and`、:keyword:`or` 和 :"
"keyword:`not`，其语义与相应的位运算符相同。支持 :class:`~pandas.Series` "
"和 :class:`~pandas.DataFrame` 对象，并且它们的行为与普通的 Python 求值"
"方式一致。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.maxframe_eval of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.maxframe_eval:12 of
msgid ""
"The expression to evaluate. This string cannot contain any Python "
"`statements <https://docs.python.org/3/reference/simple_stmts.html"
"#simple-statements>`__, only Python `expressions "
"<https://docs.python.org/3/reference/simple_stmts.html#expression-"
"statements>`__."
msgstr ""
"要计算的表达式。该字符串不能包含任何 Python `语句 <https://docs.python."
"org/3/reference/simple_stmts.html#simple-statements>`__，只能是 Python `"
"表达式 <https://docs.python.org/3/reference/simple_stmts.html#expression-"
"statements>`__。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.maxframe_eval:18 of
msgid "A dictionary of local variables, taken from locals() by default."
msgstr "本地变量的字典，默认从 locals() 获取。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.maxframe_eval:20 of
msgid "A dictionary of global variables, taken from globals() by default."
msgstr "全局变量的字典，默认从 globals() 获取。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.maxframe_eval:22 of
msgid ""
"A list of objects implementing the ``__getitem__`` special method that "
"you can use to inject an additional collection of namespaces to use for "
"variable lookup. For example, this is used in the "
":meth:`~DataFrame.query` method to inject the ``DataFrame.index`` and "
"``DataFrame.columns`` variables that refer to their respective "
":class:`~pandas.DataFrame` instance attributes."
msgstr ""
"一个实现 ``__getitem__`` 特殊方法的对象列表，您可以使用它注入额外的命名"
"空间集合以用于变量查找。例如，在 :meth:`~DataFrame.query` 方法中，会注入 "
"``DataFrame.index`` 和 ``DataFrame.columns`` 变量，它们分别引用其对应的 :"
"class:`~pandas.DataFrame` 实例属性。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.maxframe_eval:30 of
msgid ""
"The number of prior stack frames to traverse and add to the current "
"scope. Most users will **not** need to change this parameter."
msgstr ""
"要遍历并添加到当前作用域的先前堆栈帧数量。大多数用户 **不需要** 更改"
"此参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.maxframe_eval:33 of
msgid ""
"This is the target object for assignment. It is used when there is "
"variable assignment in the expression. If so, then `target` must support "
"item assignment with string keys, and if a copy is being returned, it "
"must also support `.copy()`."
msgstr ""
"这是赋值的目标对象。当表达式中存在变量赋值时使用。如果这样，那么 `target`"
" 必须支持使用字符串键进行项赋值，如果返回的是副本，则还必须支持 `.copy()`"
"。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.maxframe_eval:38 of
msgid ""
"If `target` is provided, and the expression mutates `target`, whether to "
"modify `target` inplace. Otherwise, return a copy of `target` with the "
"mutation."
msgstr ""
"如果提供了 `target`，并且表达式修改了 `target`，是否就地修改 `target`。"
"否则，返回一个带有修改的 `target` 副本。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.maxframe_eval of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.maxframe_eval of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.maxframe_eval:45 of
msgid ""
"There are many instances where such an error can be raised:          - "
"`target=None`, but the expression is multiline.     - The expression is "
"multiline, but not all them have item assignment.       An example of "
"such an arrangement is this:            a = b + 1       a + 2            "
"Here, there are expressions on different lines, making it multiline,"
"       but the last line has no variable assigned to the output of `a + "
"2`.     - `inplace=True`, but the expression is missing item assignment."
"     - Item assignment is provided, but the `target` does not support"
"       string item assignment.     - Item assignment is provided and "
"`inplace=False`, but the `target`       does not support the `.copy()` "
"method"
msgstr ""
"在许多情况下可能会引发此错误：          - `target=None`，但表达式是多行的"
"。     - 表达式是多行的，但并非所有行都有项赋值。       例如这种情况：   "
"         a = b + 1       a + 2            这里，不同行上有表达式，使其"
"成为多行，       但最后一行没有变量分配给 `a + 2` 的输出。     - `inplace"
"=True`，但表达式缺少项赋值。     - 提供了项赋值，但 `target` 不支持      "
" 字符串项赋值。     - 提供了项赋值且 `inplace=False`，但 `target`       "
"不支持 `.copy()` 方法"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.eval.maxframe_eval:49 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.query`"
msgstr ""

